title: Teams that won't return to the playoffs in 2017
itunes:title: Teams that won't return to the playoffs in 2017
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including the Saints placing Nick Fairley on the NFI list and Cam Newton throwing for the first time since his surgery. The heroes then debate which 2016 playoff teams are most likely to miss out next season.
